title: 17 wedding photos that capture sibling love
text:
The bond between siblings is unlike any other -- and that connection is especially strong on the day that one of your brothers or sisters walks down the aisle. Below, 17 photos of brides and grooms with their siblings that will warm your heart.
 Huffington Post
